{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "萧十一郎与沈璧君在玩偶世界中醒来，发现自己被缩小并囚禁于一座微型庄院。庄院主人是个侏儒，自称在此困居二十年，与雷雨、龙飞骥等武林高手同为天公子魔法的受害者。天公子以救命之恩诱骗英雄入彀，将其变为玩偶奴隶，却留下破法关键供挑战。庄主透露，献祭最珍视之物可换取自由，但二十年来无人成功。雷雨已彻底堕落，将妻子当作玩偶展示，道德尽丧。萧十一郎对牺牲与自由的抉择展现出冷酷理性的思考，沈璧君则在恐惧与厌恶中挣扎。本章揭示了天公子的恐怖控制手段和玩偶世界的诡异规则。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们怎会到这里来的？这里又是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "看来那位天公子真是个怪人！既然没有害我们的意思，为什么又要将我们迷倒后再送到这里来？我们清醒时，他难道就不能将我们送来么？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你怎么了？是不是很难受？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "没什么。只不过……我也觉得有点奇怪。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "天公子也许怕我们闲得无聊，所以将我们送到这里来，这里的书，看上三五年也未必看得完。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这地方就是我们方才看到的那栋玩偶屋子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们现在是在玩偶屋子里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但我们的人怎么会缩小了？那两个老人明明是死的玩偶，又怎会变成了活人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我们方才就想到这里来玩玩的，想不到现在居然真的如愿了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们快……快逃吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "逃到哪里去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_xiao_huan",
      "speaker_name": "红衣小鬟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敝庄主特令贱婢前来请两位到厅上去便饭小酌。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "酒尚温，请。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "请上座。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这桌酒本是庄主特地准备来为两位洗尘接风的，阁下何必还客气？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "素昧生平，怎敢叨扰？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "既已来了，就算有缘，请。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "尊姓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "萧，萧石逸。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "石逸？山石之石，飘逸之逸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下雷雨，这位……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_fei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "龙飞骥",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "那么阁下想必就是万里行云雷二侠了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我兄弟久已不在江湖走动，想不到阁下居然还记得贱名。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "无双铁掌，龙马精神——二位大名，天下皆知。十三年前天山一战，更是震惊古今，在下一向仰慕得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那已是多年前的往事了，江湖中只怕已很少有人提起。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "天山一役后，两位侠踪就未出现，江湖中人至今犹在议论纷纷，谁也猜不出两位究竟到何处去了。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "休说别人想不到，连我们自己，又何尝……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "此间已非人世，无论谁到了这里，都永无消息再至人间。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "此间已非人世？难道是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这里只不过是个玩偶的世界而已。",
      "tone": "伤感",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "玩偶？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，玩偶……其实万物，皆是玩偶，人又何尝不是玩偶？",
      "tone": "伤感",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "只不过人是天的玩偶，我们都是人的玩偶。江湖中又有谁能想到，我兄弟已做了别人的玩偶！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "庄主你……尊姓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我来此已有二十年，哪里还记得名姓？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "再过二十年，两位只怕也会将自己的名姓忘却了。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "二……二十年？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，二十年……我初来的时候，也认为这种日子简直连一天也没法忍受，要我忍受二十年，实在是无法想像。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但现在，不知不觉也过了二十年了……千古艰难惟一死，无论怎么样活着，总比死好。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位可知道自己是怎会到这里来的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下可知道自己是怎会到了这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "非但不知道，简直连相信都无法相信。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，这种事正是谁也不知道，谁也不相信的……我来此已有十二年，时时刻刻都在盼望着这只不过是场梦，但现在……现在……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_fei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "龙飞骥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但现在我们已知道，这场梦将永无醒时！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下来此之前，是否也曾有过性命之危？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "的确是死里逃生。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下的性命，是否也是被一位天公子所救的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "庄主怎会知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们也正和阁下一样，都受过那位天公子的性命之恩，只不过……",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "只不过他救我们，并不是什么好心善意，只不过是想让我们做他们的玩偶，做他的奴隶！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位可曾见过他？可知道他是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "谁也没有见过他，但到了现在，阁下想必也该知道他是个怎么样的人了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他哪里能算是个人？简直是个魔鬼！比鬼还可怕！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "此人的确具有一种不可思议的魔法，我们说的每句话，他都可能听到，我们的每件事，他都可能看到！但现在我已不再怕他！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连这种事我们都已遇着，世上还有什么更可怕的事？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，一个人若已落到如此地步，无论对任何人、任何事，都不会再有畏惧之心了。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但一个人的所做所为，若是时时刻刻都被人在瞧着，这岂非也可怕得很？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开始时，自然也觉得很不安、很难堪，但日子久了，人就渐渐变得麻木，对任何事都会觉得无所谓了。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_fei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "龙飞骥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论谁到了这里，都会变得麻木不仁、自暴自弃，因为活着也没意思，死了也没什么关系。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位为什么不想法子逃出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_fei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "龙飞骥",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "逃到哪里去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_fei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "龙飞骥",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在我们在别人眼中，已无异蝼蚁，无论任何人只要用两根手指就可以将我们捏死，我们能逃到哪里去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们若想逃出去，也并非绝对不可能。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "只要有人能破了他的魔法，我们就立刻可以恢复自由之身。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "有谁能破他的魔法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "也只有靠我们自己了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "我们自己？有什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "魔法正也和武功一样，无论多高深的武功，总有一两处破绽留下来，就连达摩易筋经都不例外，据说三丰真人就曾在其中找出了两三处破绽。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "但这魔法……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这魔法自然也有破绽，而且是天公子自己留下来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "他为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "挑战！他为的就是向我们挑战。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "挑战？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "人生正和赌博一样，若是必胜无疑，这场赌就会变得很无趣，一定要有输赢才刺激。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "天公子想必也是个很喜欢刺激的人，所以他虽用魔法将我们拘禁，却又为我们留下了一处破法的关键！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "关键就在这宅院中，只要我们能将它找出来，就能将他的魔法破解！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "这话是否他自己亲口说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，他曾亲口答应过我，无论谁破去他的魔法，他就将我们一齐释放，绝不为难。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这二十年来，我时时刻刻都在寻找，却始终未能找出那破法的关键！",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "这宅院一共只有二十七间屋子，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "若连厨房在内，是二十八间。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "那破法的关键既然就在这二十八间屋里，怎会找不出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这只因谁也猜不到那关键之物究竟是什么，也许是一粒米、一粒豆、一片木叶，也许只是一粒尘埃。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "要想找出这秘密来，固然是难如登天，但除此之外，还有个法子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "请随我来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "祭台！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "祭台？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "若有人肯将自己最心爱、最珍视之物作为祭礼献给他，他就会放了这人！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "却不知阁下最珍视的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "庄主呢？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在留在这里的人，都很自私，每个人最珍视的，就是自己的性命，谁也不愿将自己的性命献给他。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但有些人却会将别的人、别的事看得比自己性命还重。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "这种人世上并不太少。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十年前我就见到过，那是一对很恩爱的夫妻，彼此都将对方看得比自己性命还重，不幸也被天公子的魔法拘禁在这里，那丈夫出身世家，文武双全，本是个极有前途，极有希望的年轻人，但到了这里，就一切都绝望了。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "后来呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来妻子终于为丈夫牺牲了，作了天公子的祭礼，换得了她丈夫的自由和幸福。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "后来天公子真的放了她的丈夫？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "的确放了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一直没有说出他们的名字，只因我想那丈夫经过十年的奋斗，现在一定已是个很有名声，很有地位的人，我不愿他名声受损。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这对夫妇实在伟大得很……",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以我看，这夫妻两人只不过是一对呆子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "呆子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "那妻子牺牲了自己，以为可令丈夫幸福，但她的丈夫若真的将她看得比自己的性命还重，知道他的妻子为了他牺牲，他能活得心安么？他还有什么勇气奋斗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想，那丈夫现在纵然还活着，心里也必定充满了悔恨，觉得毫无生趣，说不定终日沉迷于醉乡，只望能死得快些。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他们这样做，虽然未见得是明智之举，但他们这种肯为别人牺牲自己的精神，却还是令我很佩服。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过，在这里活下去也没有什么不好，人世间的一切享受，这里都不缺少，而且绝没有世俗礼教的拘束，无论你想做什么，绝没有人管你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我们反正也落到这般地步了，能活着一天，就要好好的享受一天，什么礼教，什么名誉，全去他妈的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_mei_zi",
      "text": "梅子、小雯，我知道你们就在外面，为什么不进来？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人都是我的妻子，但你们无论谁若看上了她们，我都可以让给他的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wen",
      "text": "你不信？好。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wen",
      "text": "小雯，你身上最美的是什么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "小雯",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "是腿。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wen",
      "text": "你的腿既然很美，为什么不让大家瞧瞧？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此美腿，当饮一大杯，请。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_mei_zi",
      "text": "梅子，你呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_zi",
      "speaker_name": "梅子",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "你说我最美的是什么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_mei_zi",
      "text": "你身上处处皆美，但最美的还是你的腰。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "雷兄，你错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_mei_zi",
      "text": "她最美的地方不在腰，而在腰以上的地方。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "text": "是，的确是我错了，当浮一大白。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你看，我并没有骗你吧？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "你没有骗我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不止是我，这里每个人都和我同样慷慨的，也许比我还要慷慨多了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说的并不假，人到了这里，就不再是人了，自然也不再有羞耻之心，对任何事都会觉得无所谓。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "庄主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "两位现在也许会觉得很惊讶，很看不惯，但再过些时候，两位自然也会变得和别人一样的！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 670
    }
